{"tid":2263604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★蘋果大中華銷售急跌29%　股價盤後急挫5%","createTime":"2020-10-30T04:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T06:56:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":72,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ecde3c5d78e4aab2ad27aa2e5d8f9c43f6c25b","tid":2263604,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司（AAPL）收市後公布季績，第四財季收入和盈利雖略勝市場預期，惟大中華區業績差，以及iPhone銷售遜預期，令投資者失望。業績公布後，蘋果股價盤後時段急挫5% <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在各地收入中，惟獨大中華區銷售急跌28.6%，至79.46億美元，靠歐美及亞太其他地區的銷售，填補其缺口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2789760/【Apple業績】蘋果大中華銷售急跌29-%E3%80%80iPhone銷售遜預期\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2789760%2F%E3%80%90Apple%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE%E3%80%91%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C29-%25E3%2580%2580iPhone%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%81%9C%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=6c32d57b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2789760/【Apple業績】蘋果大中華銷售急跌29-%E3%80%80iPhone銷售遜預期</a>"},{"pid":"053e02530ddcb9d488d8932400bc77ee561ce903","tid":2263604,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d428f067cdde70d2f4e875b754aa75894140d1","tid":2263604,"uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"奶支怪 下場"},{"pid":"cd3b45950bc981ca0cc5bf56eac0fff76d6c51dd","tid":2263604,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"樓主 ifan"},{"pid":"e82ee9f2d56dbbe08e1653b9a014b2521a3c4aac","tid":22